onships|2010 Cambridge]]|ASW1x}}\n{{MedalSilver|[[2009 World Rowing Championships|2009 Pozna\u0144]]|ASW1x}}\n{{MedalSilver|[[2011 World Rowing Championships|2011 Bled]]|ASW1x}}\n{{MedalSilver|[[2019 World Rowing Championships|2019 Ottensheim]]|[[2019 World Rowing Championships \u2013 PR1 Women's single sculls|PR1W1x]]}}\n}}\n\n'''Nathalie Benoit''' is a [[French people|French]] [[Paralympian]]. She won a [[silver medal]] at the [[2012 Summer Paralympics]] in Women's [[single scull]]s [[rowing]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lequipe.fr/Aviron/Actualites/Benoit-en-argent/310365  |title=Benoit en argent |date=2 September 2012 |work=www.lequipe.fr |accessdate=2 September 2012 |language=French}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Benoit, Nathalie}}\n[[Category:French female rowers]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Date of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Knights of the National Order of Merit (France)]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 2012 Summer Paralympics]]\n[[Category:Rowers at the 2012 Summer Paralympics]]\n[[Category:Paralympic silver medalists for France]]\n[[Category:World Rowing Championships medalists for France]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing (living people)]]\n\n\n{{France-rowing-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Zyxw", "label": "safe", "comment": "add links, update article and categories", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nathalie_Benoit"}
